{
  "stem": "14552.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember her eyes, how she felt, what she must have felt to leave her child, her little child, and the one who was going to take care of that little child and her little boy.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was hard, which is a very serious understatement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we were ushered into these halls, where they took all our clothes away and they shaved our heads.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- there was the German--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Women.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Women.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were thrown-- then we were given showers and examined for some marks, for whatever lesions that we got on the trip, because they immediately would put them into the gas chamber if there were any lesions.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I saw-- through a crack in the wall, I saw my brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought I see a mirror.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was shaved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and then I see-- I look at his face, and I thought I saw a mirror, because him and I looked very much alike.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were very-- we resembled each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's very interesting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very close and-- I look at him, and I see myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we waved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was it then, that he went to the men's Auschwitz, Vernichtungslager.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we-- my sister and I went to another one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in the C Lager, C.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "C Lager, which was designated for destruction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then we were given just few meager-- just a something, a coat, I mean, or a dress, or whatever was happened to be thrown at us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we were given-- ushered into these blocks which was they held 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was 12 people to these beds with three rows of beds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was two or three.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was 3 rows of beds, 12 in each there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
